WEBVTT

00:00.665 --> 00:02.667
The question is...

00:02.668 --> 00:04.636
who am I?

00:04.637 --> 00:06.104
Right.

00:06.105 --> 00:09.130
I give you a clue, you
have a minute to guess

00:09.131 --> 00:10.865
the identity of the person in question.

00:10.866 --> 00:13.601
We must find a weapon to defeat Moloch.

00:13.602 --> 00:17.104
I fail to understand how
a game played on telephones

00:17.105 --> 00:19.340
will help us solve our
dire problem at hand.

00:19.341 --> 00:20.474
It won't.

00:20.475 --> 00:21.575
That's the point.

00:21.576 --> 00:22.843
This is a technique

00:22.844 --> 00:24.445
profilers use to crack cases

00:24.446 --> 00:25.679
when they're stuck.

00:25.680 --> 00:26.881
If you distract the conscious mind,

00:26.882 --> 00:28.149
the subconscious makes connections

00:28.150 --> 00:29.583
that you wouldn't have seen before.

00:29.584 --> 00:30.851
My mother believed

00:30.852 --> 00:32.552
that Grace Dixon hid some clues

00:32.554 --> 00:34.021
in her journal. We've gone over it

00:34.022 --> 00:35.789
so many times, you
practically memorized it,

00:35.790 --> 00:37.224
and still nada.

00:37.225 --> 00:38.859
So...

00:38.860 --> 00:40.227
you cannot tell a lie.

00:40.228 --> 00:42.429
Who are you?

00:42.430 --> 00:43.531
Oh! Oh!

00:43.532 --> 00:44.798
The little wooden puppet boy.

00:44.799 --> 00:46.834
- Pinocchio?
- Yeah.

00:46.835 --> 00:48.535
Nope. Guess again.

00:50.338 --> 00:52.106
George Washington?

00:52.107 --> 00:55.609
He was our Liar-in-Chief.

00:55.610 --> 00:57.711
He formed the Culper Spy Ring.

00:57.712 --> 00:59.246
That was a network of liars.

00:59.247 --> 01:01.815
Thank you, colonial myth buster.

01:01.816 --> 01:04.150
Ichabod.

01:04.852 --> 01:06.954
Katrina?

01:06.955 --> 01:08.722
Ichabod, can you hear me?

01:09.591 --> 01:11.392
Crane, there. The mirror.

01:15.197 --> 01:16.330
My love.

01:16.331 --> 01:18.365
- Are you in danger?
- I'm safe for now.

01:18.366 --> 01:21.101
But if Henry finds me using
this glass to speak to you, I...

01:21.102 --> 01:22.770
I failed my mission.

01:22.771 --> 01:25.205
Moloch still lives.

01:26.841 --> 01:28.873
- What happened?
- He's grown too strong.

01:28.874 --> 01:30.678
And I fear with the rate he matures,

01:30.679 --> 01:33.814
he-he could reign this Earth
in less than two days time.

01:33.815 --> 01:35.182
There is still another chance.

01:35.183 --> 01:37.384
Another way has presented itself.

01:37.385 --> 01:41.255
There is a weapon capable
of defeating Moloch.

01:41.256 --> 01:42.656
We could use your insights.

01:43.592 --> 01:44.925
What was that?

01:44.926 --> 01:46.260
I must go.

01:46.261 --> 01:49.763
No, no, Katri... Wait! Wai...

01:53.635 --> 01:56.236
We need to find the weapon.

01:58.000 --> 02:04.074
Advertise your product or brand here
